{"tid":137750,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"高中生尾隨非禮11歲女童被捕","createTime":"2017-02-28T05:17:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-01T00:01:19.000Z","uid":26658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"78394b88fab621a334f99a91940dc6c7eeb76a99","tid":137750,"uid":26658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T05:17:13.000Z","msg":"【澳門日報消息】司警偵破1宗性脅迫案，拘捕1名17歲本地高中男學生。<br />\n<br />\n案情透露，本月24日下午6時，11歲本地小學女生放學返回學校附近沙梨頭南街的住所，被住其他大廈的疑犯尾隨，疑犯與事主進入升降機後，按事主單位下2層的樓層，再經後樓梯跑上事主住所的樓層扮偶遇，查問大廈的補習社位置。由於疑犯身穿校服，故事主沒有戒心。突然疑犯發狂將事主推入後樓梯，對事主上下其手，事主呼叫和大哭，疑犯立即逃走。<br />\n<br />\n翌日，事主在家人陪同下向治安警察局報案，本月27日治安警警員到北區某學校帶走疑犯，交司警處理。疑犯承認一時衝動犯案。案件已通報教青局。<br />\n<br />\n司警表示性脅迫罪罪成可判2至8年徒刑，被害人未滿14歲屬加重情節，加3分之1刑期。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://h5.newaircloud.com/news_detail?newsid=1153962_aomen&amp;app=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fh5.newaircloud.com%2Fnews_detail%3Fnewsid%3D1153962_aomen%26app%3D1&d=W0WGn%2FLYmVT4dQ5oB2FXDW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=3695b13f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://h5.newaircloud.com/news_detail?newsid=1153962_aomen&amp;app=1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/175Lq1N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F175Lq1N.jpg&h=5563dab9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/28/131652_fc7733d8364d762198b23db84d3b2941.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F28%2F131652_fc7733d8364d762198b23db84d3b2941.jpg&h=f9837da2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n澳門得一分<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5bf9f7c5edec4adac164944bb6d337da47dfc0f","tid":137750,"uid":26658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T06:47:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ad57c2264ef5c7ab0f58c5825c78c3820b78e19","tid":137750,"uid":26658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T16:43:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f92989e6264919bb7646e8d8823f47690a10e3f","tid":137750,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T23:28:47.000Z","msg":"當當正正溝 可以扑添啦<br />\n等多幾年"},{"pid":"ca1e97e57a499c10936bf69c22cd220de2ab9a28","tid":137750,"uid":50328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T00:01:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}